Pseudocode 1
Ask user for phrase
store that phrase in empty RESULT string
check each letter in the phrase once
  if character is lowercase fine its ASCII value
  add the changed character to the Result string
otherwise
  add the character as is to the RESULT string
Print the RESULT string after all characters are processed

Pseudocode 2
Ask user to enter first number
  store users first number
ask user to enter second number
  strore users second number
Add first number + second number
Get Result
Print the Result

